data.description: Welcome to your dream property, This enchanting estate boasts an array of features that will capture your heart and make you feel right at home, OVER 2 acres of breathtaking land. As you arrive, a long, driveway lined with towering trees welcomes you to your private oasis. Step inside and prepare to be mesmerized by the timeless elegance of this residence. The main living area is adorned with a sunken-in living room, a unique architectural gem that adds depth and character to the space with two living rooms, you'll have plenty of room to entertain guests! In addition to the covered garages, a detached garage, a work shop provides ample room for storing vehicles, recreational equipment, or even DIY projects with ease in this dedicated space designed to inspire. Don't miss out on the chance to own this remarkable RARE gem on over 2 acres.
